textAfterTable: Category Key General "In 2011, registered voters in the City of Idaho Falls elected to create an Auditorium District for the direct purpose of constructing and maintaining a multi-purpose event center that will deliver multiple benefits to our community. The Event Center will provide new options for entertainment and will provide several short and long-term business opportunities while pumping millions of dollars into the local economy. Entertainment Benefits The Idaho Falls Event Center will attract professional entertainment and offer incredible opportunities for residents of Eastern Idaho.   Read more… Economic Benefits The Idaho Falls Events Center will provide short- and long-term economic benefits for Idaho Falls and be a major economic force in Eastern Idaho.
